00:47:13.990 --> 00:47:18.669
one of the more productive ways

00:47:20.349 --> 00:47:22.300
for spam prevention

00:47:23.080 --> 00:47:26.409
rather than our CAPTCHAs
and our reCAPTCHAs and stuff like that.

00:47:26.410 --> 00:47:28.040
But that is one
of the more successful ways

00:47:28.040 --> 00:47:29.040
